{"tid":2243678,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐洲議會40名成員發聯名信  要求把華為中興定為高風險供應商","createTime":"2020-10-15T02:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T05:00:52.000Z","uid":204533,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"04b1cebbbdfaa1dfa6a71a60e583050413c3133e","tid":2243678,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲議會40多名成員在一份聯署信函中強調說，中國通信公司華為和中興都是高風險供應商，對歐洲的網絡安全構成安全威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美國政治網站（Politico）報導說，這些代表五個政治團體的議會成員們在一封致歐盟成員國通信部長和歐盟委員會高級官員的信中做出瞭如上表述。<strong><span class=\"red\">有40多名歐洲議會成員參加了聯署，包括歐洲委員會前副主席安西普（Andrus Ansip）、歐洲議會對華關係代表團團長彼蒂科費爾（Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer）和其他黨派的知名成員。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n信函指出，&quot;與所有中國公司一樣，（華為和相對較小的中國對手中興）根據中國法律都必須執行中國非民主極權政府的指令。這包括利用網絡來控製本國人民以及對西方政府、公司和民眾進行間諜活動。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n信函強調，&ldquo;因此毫無疑問，華為和中興都是'高風險'供應商，其在歐洲5G網絡中的科技將會構成安全威脅&rdquo;，&ldquo;5G網絡需要確保技術健康的安全解決方案，排除被列入'高風險'類別的供應商接觸網絡敏感的部分。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n信函要求歐盟和國家公共基金進行評估，確保&ldquo;任何歐洲資金、即納稅人的錢都不會用於使用'高風險'通信設備供應商的技術。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n議員們還在信函中批評中國未能向愛立信和諾基亞等歐洲供應商開放國內的通信市場，&ldquo;歐盟和中國在5G供應商的市場准入方面還明顯缺乏對等。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n議員們說，歐盟應該就國際採購機制（International Procurement Instrument）草案達成一致，對限制歐洲公司市場准入的國家的公司關閉歐盟的公共採購。<br />\n<br />\n議員們並要求成員國政府&ldquo;對'高風險'供應商進行聯合評估和分類&rdquo;，對華為和中興的定位達成共識。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/eu-brand-huawei-high-risk-vendor-10142020/5622148.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Feu-brand-huawei-high-risk-vendor-10142020%2F5622148.html&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiYBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=55a5625f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/eu-brand-huawei-high-risk-vendor-10142020/5622148.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"44b9769d843048a1f46ed41845fbdc07d4900ea3","tid":2243678,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20cbf7f76339bb8af8cb10ed1897345ac0530f4","tid":2243678,"uid":295459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68ed3725388684659165ba8310e1251f8efcb34","tid":2243678,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113cd8bde4cd31a721bd8ea4edca6362bfd0c6ed","tid":2243678,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1117888a7f606687e755ea4f542b317b80107504","tid":2243678,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"4年前歐洲: DONALD TRUMP痴線!<br />\n4年後歐洲: 仲唔出招? 痴線!<br />\n不過仲有十幾日 CHINA JOE就當選美國特首 <br />\n然歐盟又再一次走錯邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62470a77a8cfb7431aff5b9cfaa36a0f7c7d9e62","tid":2243678,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T02:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d5be34007922e393f227b8c4e33ba8de2a5c79","tid":2243678,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s